flowchart LR
    A[User starts registration] --> B[System validates basic details]
    B --> C{Role type}
    
    C -->|Admin| D[Business details check]
    C -->|Field Agent| E[Passkey + Profile verification]
    C -->|Customer| F[Customer profile verification]

    D --> G[Duplicate account check]
    E --> G
    F --> G

    G --> H{Already exists?}
    H -->|Yes| X[Registration rejected with clear reason]
    H -->|No| I[Create user account]

    I --> J[Link operational profile if required]
    J --> K[Consume passkey if used]
    K --> L[Issue login token]
    L --> M[Registration successful]